snippet.title: Contraption Maker Trailer
snippet.description:
Contraption Maker is available at http://contraptionmaker.com/

Come join the fun and solve over 200 official puzzles, or make your own ridiculous contraption in the Maker Lab. Share your creations with the rest of the world through the Workshop.

Background music in the first half of this trailer "The Cannery", Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
